Covenant Obi Osborne Dave who is the son of Governor David Umahi of Ebonyi is a man of many sides.  Osborn as he is fondly called by close friends is a student born March 14, 1998, in a city of Port- Harcourt.  At a young age, he became the MD of Brass oil & Construction Company, as well as the Chief Executive Officer of Lapalm Royal Resort.  The young entrepreneur had started high school early at the age of 8 and recently graduated from the University of Surrey in the United Kingdom at 21.  He is now proudly a bachelor’s degree holder after he bagged the certificate in civil engineering.  Obi Osborne moved to London when he was 15 and has so far recorded  great achievements within his youthful age.